a friend to yourself.

893
01:11:26.983 --> 01:11:29.768
You don't have that.
This is too much.

894
01:11:31.422 --> 01:11:35.774
No. we got 60. 70 years of this?

895
01:11:39.387 --> 01:11:40.736
