before he talked her
into leaving.

934
01:15:06.332 --> 01:15:08.683
Did he drive you here?
Is he outside?

935
01:15:08.726 --> 01:15:11.076
No. He's in Maryland.

936
01:15:14.689 --> 01:15:16.691
Does he know you're here?

937
01:15:16.734 --> 01:15:18.344
Yeah. he let me know
